        public Position translate(Position displacement)
        Create a new point that is the result of translating this instance in direction specified by "displacement". Put another way, return the "sum" of these two points.
        Parameters:
        displacement - A point describing how far to translate this point.
        Returns:
        A new point that is the result of the translation.

      • getNeighbors

        public java.util.Set<Position> getNeighbors()
        Returns a set of possible neighbors of this position. They're not guaranteed actually to exist (for instance, the neighbors of (0, 0) include (-1, 0) and (0, -1), which are likely to be invalid.).
